OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1784099888
OL,3,CNew police images released to mark
OL,4,C25th anniversary of Peter Falconio's
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,FPolice in Australia have marked the
OL,8,F25th anniversary of the murder of
OL,9,FBritish backpacker and Brighton
OL,10,Fstudent Peter Falconio by releasing
OL,11,Fnew images from their investigation,
OL,12,Fin the hope it "could lead police to
OL,13,FPeter's remains".
OL,15,FBradley John Murdoch was convicted in
OL,16,F2005 of murdering Mr Falconio, 28, and
OL,17,Fassaulting his girlfriend Joanne Lees
OL,18,Fat gunpoint on a remote stretch of
OL,19,Froad near Barrow Creek in Australia's
OL,20,FNorthern Territory on July 14 2001.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/8
