CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1784099888
OL,3,CNew police images released to mark
OL,4,C25th anniversary of Peter Falconio's
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,FMr Falconio and Ms Lees, both from
OL,8,FHuddersfield, West Yorkshire, were
OL,9,Ftravelling across the country in a
OL,10,Fcamper van when they were ambushed by
OL,11,FMurdoch on the isolated Stuart Highway.
OL,13,FMurdoch was convicted and sentenced to
OL,14,Flife imprisonment without parole for
OL,15,Fat least 28 years.
OL,17,FHe died in prison last year after
OL,18,Fbeing diagnosed with terminal throat
OL,19,Fcancer in 2019, but never revealed the
OL,20,Flocation of Mr Falconio's remains.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
