OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1784099888
OL,3,CNew police images released to mark
OL,4,C25th anniversary of Peter Falconio's
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,FTo mark 25 years since Mr Falconio's
OL,8,Fmurder, Northern Territory Police have
OL,9,Freleased previously unseen images from
OL,10,Fthe case.
OL,12,FPictures include vision of Ms Lees
OL,13,Fphotographed hours after the attack,
OL,14,Fthe orange Volkswagen Kombi van driven
OL,15,Fby the couple, and an image of Murdoch
OL,16,Fstaring straight at a camera during
OL,17,Fthe police investigation.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1784099888
OL,3,CNew police images released to mark
OL,4,C25th anniversary of Peter Falconio's
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,FNorthern Territory Police Force
OL,8,Fcommissioner Martin Dole APM said the
OL,9,Fforce would exhaust every possibility
OL,10,Fto find Mr Falconio's remains and
OL,11,Fbring closure to his loved ones.
OL,13,F"This was a traumatic and horrific
OL,14,Fevent for Ms Lees, and for Peter's
OL,15,Ffamily, who have now gone such a long
OL,16,Ftime without the answers they
OL,17,Fdeserve," he said.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1784099888
OL,3,CNew police images released to mark
OL,4,C25th anniversary of Peter Falconio's
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,F"While a murderer has been held
OL,8,Faccountable for his crimes, this
OL,9,Finvestigation can never be considered
OL,10,Fclosed until Peter's remains are found
OL,11,Fand his family can lay him to rest.
OL,13,F"It is deeply regrettable that Murdoch
OL,14,Fdied without, as far as we know, ever
OL,15,Fdisclosing the location of Peter's
OL,16,Fremains. His cowardly silence has
OL,17,Fdenied his family, friends and loved
OL,18,Fones the closure they deserve."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1784099888
OL,3,CNew police images released to mark
OL,4,C25th anniversary of Peter Falconio's
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,FHe continued: "Twenty-five years is a
OL,8,Fsignificant milestone, and the
OL,9,FNorthern Territory Police Force
OL,10,Fremains committed to bringing this
OL,11,Finvestigation to its fullest
OL,12,Fconclusion and will continue to pursue
OL,13,Fevery avenue available.
OL,15,F"For many investigators, this case has
OL,16,Fspanned decades of their policing
OL,17,Fcareers. Their commitment to finding
OL,18,FPeter and delivering answers to his
OL,19,Ffamily has never wavered.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1784099888
OL,3,CNew police images released to mark
OL,4,C25th anniversary of Peter Falconio's
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,F"The release of new footage could lead
OL,8,Fpolice to Peter's remains.
OL,10,F"There may still be someone who knows
OL,11,Fsomething, whether that be information
OL,12,Fthey have never previously shared with
OL,13,Fpolice or something Murdoch said to
OL,14,Fthem.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1784099888
OL,3,CNew police images released to mark
OL,4,C25th anniversary of Peter Falconio's
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,F"We continue to urge anyone with
OL,8,Finformation relating to the location
OL,9,Fof Peter Falconio's remains to come
OL,10,Fforward. No piece of information is
OL,11,Ftoo small; what may seem insignificant
OL,12,Fcould prove critical in helping
OL,13,Finvestigators finally resolve this
OL,14,Fcase."
OL,16,FA reward of up to 500,000 Australian
OL,17,Fdollars (#260,000) has been offered
OL,18,Ffor any information that leads
OL,19,Fdirectly to the discovery of Mr
OL,20,FFalconio's remains.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
